The Sailing Ships and other poems (1918)
The Happy Foreigner (1920)
Serena Blandish or the Difficulty of Getting Married (1924)
Alice & Thomas & Jane (1930)
National Velvet (1935)
The Door of Life (1938)
The Squire (1938, suom. Elämän ovi, 1939)
Lottie Dundass (1943, näytelmä)
Two Plays (1944)
The Loved and Envied (1951, suom. Rakastettu – kadehdittu, 1953)
Theatre (1951)
The Girl’s Journey (1954)
The Chalk Garden (1955, näytelmä)
The Chinese Prime Minister (1964, näytelmä)
A Matter of Gravity (1967, näytelmä)
Autobiography (1969)
Four Plays (1970)
Poems (1978)
Letters to Frank Harris & Other Friends (1980)
Early Poems (1987)

